# Quick script showing the power of python

From start to completion in 15 minutes, including finding the Growl python bindings and determining how it works


Dependencies:
- BeautifulSoup
- Growl (osx / windows) 


Use:
- Specify a target url to crawl in __init__ method 
  (default set to "http://www.stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/django)

- run script: `python stack_overflow_checker`
- run as cronjob every X minutes.